Supergirl (000 - 033) (2011 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Megan, G85 & Nahga-Empire) 

Supergirl (Volume 6)

A "New 52" initiative book starring Kara Zor-El, as Supergirl. It showcases her first moments on Earth and her discovery of how much time has passed. Plus, her very first encounter with Superman.

Collected Editions

Vol. 1: Last Daughter of Krypton (#1-7)
Vol. 2: Girl in the World (#0 and 8-12)
Vol. 3: Sanctuary (#13-19)
Superman: H'el On Earth (#14-17)
Vol. 4: Out of the Past (#21-26)


Another fully digital update to my earlier current ongoing series packs - Updating all these packs from a few months back using all Empire digital issues (HD where available)
